data.description: This charming single-family home is located at 2254 SW 4th St. in Cape Coral, FL. the property offers a comfortable living space of 1,665 sq.ft. Step inside the front door and be welcomed by a large great room with cathedral ceilings and sliders to the screened lanai. Outside the lanai is a fenced yard with plenty of room for a pool! The home is a split bedroom floor plan with master to the left of the great room, laundry room off the kitchen, and bedrooms 2 & 3 along with the guest bathroom, to the right. Ideal for a family looking for a cozy and well-maintained property, this home provides a balance of functionality and comfort. Storm panels, new roof in 2019, new A/C in 2022, along with ALL ASSESSMENTS PAID IN FULL, make this home a must buy. Pre approved buyers make your offer today.
